title: the gals are back!  danielle’s NYC visit & moving plans

description:
Brooke and Danielle are LIVE from Brooke’s apartment in NYC after over a year of being apart!!!  The gals are talking about Danielle’s trip to the city with Ryan, Danielle’s moving plans, Ryan’s moving plans, and overall highs and lows from the weekend. Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/screenshots!
